OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,FJersey's Council of Ministers are to
OL,7,Fmeet on Friday to discuss how to
OL,8,Fproceed with choosing its next ferry
OL,9,Foperator.
OL,11,FGuernsey made the shock announcement
OL,12,Fon Wednesday that it would be picking
OL,13,FCondor, owned by Brittany Ferries.
OL,15,FHowever, Jersey's Economic Development
OL,16,FMinister says this does not mean the
OL,17,Fisland will not be rushed into making
OL,18,Fits own decision.
