OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,FIt comes amid reports that Condor
OL,7,Fasked the government for a loan of
OL,8,F#80M in the last year, with #10M
OL,9,Fneeded up front to secure their
OL,10,Fservices. This was allegedly rejected
OL,11,Fat the time.
OL,13,FWatch the full interview here...
OL,15,FWhen asked if he would pursue another
OL,16,Foperator if he can't get a guarantee
OL,17,Fthat Jersey taxpayers will not be
OL,18,Fresponsible for picking up a potential
OL,19,Frescue deal, he replied: "There's
OL,20,Flogic in that but not something I'm
OL,21,Fwilling to say at the moment."
