OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,FDeputy Morel also added: "I'm not
OL,7,Fgoing to be pulled at the minute one
OL,8,Fway or the other (with who Jersey will
OL,9,Fselect). What I want to make sure is
OL,10,Fwhoever we appoint that they have the
OL,11,Ffinancial stability to last that 15
OL,12,Fyears, that really is for me the
OL,13,Fbottom line."
OL,15,FThe Minister then said: "I'm not angry
OL,16,Fwith Guernsey. I do understand that
OL,17,Fdifferent jurisdictions and different
OL,18,Fcountries have to look at their own
OL,19,Finterests.
