OL,3,CJersey's Council of Ministers meeting
OL,4,Cto discuss ferry dilemma
OL,6,F"Guernsey has its perspective and
OL,7,Fthat's absolutely fine, but I am
OL,8,Fdetermined that Jersey tax payers know
OL,9,FI am acting for their benefit and on
OL,10,Ftheir behalf. That's the thing that
OL,11,Freally matters to me."
OL,13,FAfter this, he said he couldn't give a
OL,14,Ftimescale on when the decision would
OL,15,Fbe made.
